{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaba453f7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s12552"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12552"},"text":"§ 12552.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Funeral honors functions at funerals for veterans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Performance by a Reserve of funeral honors functions at the funeral of a veteran (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s1491/h"},"text":"section 1491(h) of this title","children":[],"tail":") may not be considered to be a period of drill or training, but may be performed as funeral honors duty under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s12503"},"text":"section 12503 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaba453f8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/261/dA/tV/s567/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–261, div. A, title V, § 567(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2031"},"text":"112 Stat. 2031","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/dA/tV/s578/g/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, div. A, title V, § 578(g)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/628"},"text":"113 Stat. 628","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dA"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [[div. A]","children":[],"tail":", title X, § 1087(a)(21)], "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-30"},"text":"Oct. 30, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1654"},"text":"114 Stat. 1654","children":[],"tail":", 1654A–291.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaba453f9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaba453fa-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idaba453fb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2000—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398","children":[],"tail":" inserted period at end."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65","children":[],"tail":" substituted “honors functions at funerals for veterans” for “honor guard functions: prohibition of treatment as drill or training” in section catchline and amended text generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “Performance by a Reserve of honor guard functions at the funeral of a veteran may not be considered to be a period of drill or training otherwise required.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
